subproject.description:
Project objectives:
- to strengthen the implementation of UN Cares Programme, 
- to enhance the national capacity for strategic planning, costing and budgeting, and M&E, 
- to support activities aiming at reducing stigma and discrimination and promoting gender and human rights of PLWH.
